{"tid":695040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"穿和服遊京都被內地客意淫 內地女直斥「當場噁心到想吐」","createTime":"2018-06-09T01:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T05:36:20.000Z","uid":184679,"like":32,"dislike":178,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"8b0f7efc20b105597b75813eec84ebd7af93dab3","tid":695040,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T01:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bm9zSl54cu7PVRFcRMwYGg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/https://media.zenfs.com/creatr-images/GLB/2018-06-08/60339fe0-6b28-11e8-8a8b-03b876ca5da4_5b19eecc3088d324182cd2c4_201806081049.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fbm9zSl54cu7PVRFcRMwYGg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fcreatr-images%2FGLB%2F2018-06-08%2F60339fe0-6b28-11e8-8a8b-03b876ca5da4_5b19eecc3088d324182cd2c4_201806081049.jpg&h=6cb26498&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">李玖肆穿和服玩京都 (網上圖片)</span><br />\n<br />\n一名內地女子日前到日本京都旅遊，更穿上和服在街上漫步，豈料2名內地旅客竟以為她不懂中文，在她背後發表猥褻言論，讓她十分憤怒，直斥「當場噁心到想吐」。她把事件在微博發表彼惹起爭論，最終女事主把有關微博刪除。<br />\n<br />\n該名女子是內地知名微博主李玖肆，她日前與男友前往日本旅遊，來到京都後換上和服拍照，豈料有2名內地遊客在她背後評頭品足，更聲稱「看這些穿和服的，逮兩個強姦了她們跑都跑不掉，哈哈哈哈。」李玖肆當場感到極度氣憤，還回頭向2人翻白眼。<br />\n<br />\n她事後更在微博直斥「我當場噁心到想吐，從腳趾到頭頂感到丟人透了」，她又指，雖然不知道2名男子的口音是哪裡柩的，「但確實來自厲害了我的國」。<br />\n<br />\n博文一出引起內地網民熱議，不少人感嘆「這種人很多，真的超噁」、「重點是他們還不覺得自己有錯」。不過也有人認為「這種事沒必要上升到國家吧」，甚至有人反罵道「吃的國家的、穿的國家的，還有臉在這裡罵，有本事滾出中國」，但遭李玖肆回擊「在大庭廣眾之下大聲討論出來，我只見過這一個」。由於事件惹起軒然大波，李玖肆最終把有關微博刪除。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%A9%BF%E5%92%8C%E6%9C%8D%E9%81%8A%E4%BA%AC%E9%83%BD%E8%A2%AB%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%A2%E6%84%8F%E6%B7%AB-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%A5%B3%E7%9B%B4%E6%96%A5-%E7%95%B6%E5%A0%B4%E5%99%81%E5%BF%83%E5%88%B0%E6%83%B3%E5%90%90-083200890.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25A9%25BF%25E5%2592%258C%25E6%259C%258D%25E9%2581%258A%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E9%2583%25BD%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%2584%258F%25E6%25B7%25AB-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%2596%25A5-%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%2599%2581%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%2583%25B3%25E5%2590%2590-083200890.html&d=RXqriQOFW%2F1LyN3qRmJbrcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=0992eec0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%A9%BF%E5%92%8C%E6%9C%8D%E9%81%8A%E4%BA%AC%E9%83%BD%E8%A2%AB%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%A2%E6%84%8F%E6%B7%AB-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%A5%B3%E7%9B%B4%E6%96%A5-%E7%95%B6%E5%A0%B4%E5%99%81%E5%BF%83%E5%88%B0%E6%83%B3%E5%90%90-083200890.html</a><br />\n<br />\n中國人不X中國人, 一場誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa4bebbfd1bb48bec2f056f923aae276217e7a14","tid":695040,"uid":122155,"like":286,"dislike":1,"score":285,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T01:53:43.000Z","msg":"但確實來自厲害了我的國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n泱泱大國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512defb7dbe37821288b76f52f6f1bd06ad3d353","tid":695040,"uid":120715,"like":7,"dislike":34,"score":-27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T01:57:57.000Z","msg":"其實有幾多日本人會唔係節慶都穿和服"},{"pid":"61abeeffa72a92f9ccaac2d759cdf8f76122757a","tid":695040,"uid":122155,"like":211,"dislike":1,"score":210,"quote":{"pid":"8b0f7efc20b105597b75813eec84ebd7af93dab3","tid":695040,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T01:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bm9zSl54cu7PVRFcRMwYGg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/https://media.zenfs.com/creatr-images/GLB/2018-06-08/60339fe0-6b28-11e8-8a8b-03b876ca5da4_5b19eecc3088d324182cd2c4_201806081049.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fbm9zSl54cu7PVRFcRMwYGg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.